## Next Steps
Once deployed to Vercel:
1. The Analytics will automatically start tracking page views
2. Visit your Vercel dashboard > Analytics to enable the feature
3. Data will appear in the dashboard after users visit your site
4. You can verify the integration by checking the browser's Network tab for requests to `/_vercel/insights/*`

